  "reference_number": "GAC0049",
  "remarks": "\nAgnes Nandutu is an involved person under the Global Anti-Corruption Sanctions Regulations 2021 on the basis that there are reasonable grounds to suspect that she, as a foreign public official, has been involved in serious corruption. Specifically, that NANDUTU, whilst State Minister for Karamoja Affairs, engaged in serious corruption by having a role in or supporting the improper diversion, grant or allocation of iron sheets for the benefit of others. \n",
